inNumbers.title: Points
inNumbers.description: The combined total number of points scored by both teams throughout the entire match.

inNumbers.title: Duration
inNumbers.description: The total length of the match, from the first serve through until the last point has ended.

inNumbers.title: Spectators
inNumbers.description: Total number of people in attendance at the venue – taken at the end of the second set.

inNumbers.title: Match Spikes
inNumbers.description: The combined total number of successful spikes achieved by both teams throughout the entire match.

inNumbers.title: Reception Level
inNumbers.description: An average of the two team service reception percentages from the complete match.

inNumbers.title: Net Domination
inNumbers.description: The number of successful point winning blocks of RC CANNES compared to Savino Del Bene SCANDICCI.

inNumbers.title: Ace Count
inNumbers.description: RC CANNES number of service aces compared to Savino Del Bene SCANDICCI

inNumbers.title: Error Difference
inNumbers.description: Errors leading to points of RC CANNES, next to those from Savino Del Bene SCANDICCI
